data.description: We Welcome you Home to this beautiful community of Berry Creek Highlands. This wonderful Ashton Woods 1 story home, is like new just built in early 2023. Home features. 4 bedrooms, spacious living room, & private study and that’s just the start. The open and desirable floor plan welcomes you from the moment you step through the door, with Open island kitchen featuring SS appliances, granite countertops, beautiful tile backsplash and ample cabinet space. Spend your evenings and weekends on your covered back patio enjoying time with all your family and friends. Minutes from recreation, parks, dining, shopping, and entertainment. Zoned to Jarrell ISD.
